## Ingredients

- [ ] 2 oz (60 ml) Brandy
- [ ] 10oz (30 ml) Cointreau
- [ ] 1/2 oz (5 ml) lemon juice

## Recipe

1. Combine in a shaker over ice
1. Shake until well mixed
1. Strain and serve in a cocktail glass

